  {
    "text": "It is imperative\nthat we reimagine",
    "start": "1200",
    "end": "3300"
  },
  {
    "text": "our capitalist markets\nto create a more",
    "start": "3300",
    "end": "5700"
  },
  {
    "text": "inclusive and sustainable\nform of capitalism that",
    "start": "5700",
    "end": "8760"
  },
  {
    "text": "works for every\nperson and the planet.",
    "start": "8760",
    "end": "11220"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our world and its climate are\non the verge of profound changes",
    "start": "11220",
    "end": "15000"
  },
  {
    "text": "as the result of our\nglobal economic activities.",
    "start": "15000",
    "end": "17820"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our goal with\nImpact-Weighted Accounts",
    "start": "17820",
    "end": "19980"
  },
  {
    "text": "is to drive the creation\nof financial accounts",
    "start": "19980",
    "end": "22920"
  },
  {
    "text": "that reflect a company's\nfinancial, social, and",
    "start": "22920",
    "end": "26520"
  },
  {
    "text": "environmental performance,\nand motivates investor",
    "start": "26520",
    "end": "29700"
  },
  {
    "text": "and managerial decision-making.",
    "start": "29700",
    "end": "31470"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our actions have\nconsequences not only",
    "start": "31470",
    "end": "34140"
  },
  {
    "text": "for financial and\nphysical capital,",
    "start": "34140",
    "end": "35850"
  },
  {
    "text": "but also for human, social,\nand natural capital.",
    "start": "35850",
    "end": "39359"
  },
  {
    "text": "Is this ambitious?",
    "start": "39360",
    "end": "40470"
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes, but not unrealistic.",
    "start": "40470",
    "end": "42330"
  },
  {
    "text": "Indeed, companies are\nalready making efforts",
